Web3 Event Ticketing L1
Overview

Web3 Event Ticketing L1 is designed to power decentralized ticketing platforms that eliminate fraud, scalping, and counterfeit tickets.

Features

NFT-based ticket issuance

Anti-scalping mechanisms

Event access verification

Secondary market royalty rules

Fraud-resistant ticket ownership

Architecture
Ticket Minting Engine

Creates verifiable digital tickets.

Ownership Registry

Stores ticket ownership on-chain.

Transfer Rules Module

Controls resale conditions.

Event Validation Layer

Verifies entry permissions.

Use Cases

Concert ticketing

Sports events

Conferences and festivals

Digital event access
